</div>

<p class="black bold mt1 mb1">
  All transfer requests processed Monday-Thursday before 1pm PT will be
  completed within 1 day, typically in 8 hours.
</p>
<p class="secondary h5 mt0">
  Transfer requests processed Friday-Sunday can take 3-5 days to complete
  depending on the time of day your request is processed. Sadly, this is
  beyond our control, constrained by the US banking / ACH transfer system.
</p>
<p class="secondary h5 mt0">
  Please plan accordingly.
</p>

<article class="card mt3">
  <%= render 'form', emburse_transfer: @emburse_transfer %>
